relevant_findings.cardiac: Regular rate and rhythm, S1/S2, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs
relevant_findings.lung: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, or rhonchi, breathing comfortably without use of accessory muscles
relevant_findings.abdomen: Nondistended, bowel sounds positive, nontender in all quadrants, no rebound/guarding, no hepatosplenomegaly
relevant_findings.extremities: Moving all extremities well, no cyanosis, clubbing, or edema
relevant_findings.skin: Slightly jaundiced, warm and well perfused, no excoriations or lesions, no rashes
